                                     0.2.0


ASCII Combat is an arcade game about killing ASCII characters. It's an indie
game, so you've probably never heard of it. ASCII Combat is written entirely in
C, using the ncurses toolkit.

For more information about ASCII Combat and its game mechanics, see:

    >implying there's a project web page

